## Summary

- ‚úÖ ALWAYS use `usePublicUrl` hook for S3-stored images
- ‚úÖ Pass the S3 key to the hook, get back `data?.url`
- ‚úÖ Use the fetched URL in `<AvatarImage>`, `<img>`, or other image components
- ‚úÖ Handle missing keys gracefully (`?? ""` for the hook, conditional rendering for the src)
- ‚ùå NEVER use raw S3 keys directly as image `src`
